4.5 Operations - Counter

4.5.1 Increment





form
code
live




(do (var x 1) (:++ x) x)
let x = 1;
++x;
x;
2







4.5.2 Increment By





form
code
live




(do (var x 1) (:+= x 10) x)
let x = 1;
x += 10;
x;
